Title: Determining Microbial Prevalence Cutoff
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Priscila Dobbler, Luiz Roesch
Maintainer: Priscila Dobbler <prisciladobbler@gmail.com>
Description: This package identifies the best cutoff for microbial prevalence. It splits phyloseq objects based on variables,
    computes prevalences based 
    Best prevalence cutoff based on Out of Bag error from RandomForests.
